    public interface Releasable
    Interface supporting object release. Release should release all resources currently associated with the object; use of the Object following disposal is will re-initialize resources as needed. The Object should be able to cycle between the released and initialized state without restriction during the lifetime of the object.
    See Also:
    com.atakmap.util.Disposable
